3fecf3f03d298991b916db2c783b753fd9abe66e7bd33304a57c36aaf27f9e35236b8ea05676edb280326c02fcf2ca6acf7d1b10e329e16feea8b1c24c43e428  fix-compilation-on-musl.patch"
